pullRequest.body:
In this PR, we package the technical assumptions that are needed for the small object argument in a typeclass `IsCardinalForSmallObjectArgument I Îº` where `I` is a class of morphisms and `Îº` is a suitable regular cardinal. In a follow-up PR, it shall be proved that `HasFunctorialFactorization I.rlp.llp I.rlp` holds.

---

- [x] depends on: #21849
- [x] depends on: #21843
